cc:Work.dc:title: Shiny green/red voting arrows
cc:Work.dc:description: I needed a set of arrows for the Drupal Voting API module, and Voxxi's Crystal Download Icon was exactly what I was looking for. The svg features 4 icons, 2 of each (up/down), and 2 greyscale, 2 colour (green/red). Each icon sits flush with each other for easy css integration (ie, a single png file for all button states). The icon has been modified from the original to include a darker outline around both button and arrow symbols.
